SUPPLY: Start one Supply unit per turn,
maximum, in Brittany box in addition to
those started for Division HQ starts.
1. Add one Supply Unit for each Division HQ started on this chart.
2. Initial pool of Supply Units = 18; seven on map and 11 on this chart.
Maximum size of pool = 57 units in play (58 if 319th Division is used).
3. Supply Units that start on this chart may not move until 7 June turn.
4. One Supply Unit per turn may be started from the pool in the Brittany box.
